She won’t come with us... Nurse Prabha
doesn’t like movies.
NURSE 1 (O.S.)
Please Nurse! You must come!
PRABHA
(smiling)
You girls go ahead....
A murmur of disappointment.
The nurses continue their chatter. Prabha finishes her lunch and hastily packs
