Ouch!
The Male Nurse recoils backwards, holding his forearm.
MALE NURSE (CONT’D)
(defeated)
She bit me.
Prabha turns back to Kaki sternly. She has had enough.
She marches towards the older woman. She stares down at her. Kaki is now
