wearing her stiff sari uniform but a casual lavender salwar-kameez. A loose
duppata hangs over her. She opens the window, letting the cool wind touch her
face.
The sound of the rumbling bus turns into a moan of the wind.
Anu, is wearing a casual ochre yellow blouse, sitting next to Prabha in the bus.
